mc-nbt-edit by sakisds <sakisds@gmx.com>
Uses the NBT library by Thomas Woolford <woolford.thomas@gmail.com>
Based on the NBT specifications by Markus Persson


This script is editing the level.dat files inside Minecraft's maps to change some settings.

So far it can only do toogle two settings:
-Game Mode: Determinates if the map is for Creative or Survival mode
-Hardcore: Enables or disabled hardcore mode for this map

For usage please use the --help option.
